# <a name="saving-messages-in-outlookcom"></a><span data-ttu-id="37956-102">Ziņojumu saglabāšanas Outlook.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-102">Saving messages in Outlook.com</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="37956-103">Outlook.com nevar saglabāt e-pasta ziņojumus, bet tos var izdrukāt PDF formātā, kuras var saglabāt jūsu datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-103">You cannot save email messages in Outlook.com, but you can print them to a PDF which you can save on your PC.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="37956-104">Microsoft drukātu uz PDF utilīts, kas ir iekļauts Windows 10 ļauj drukāt jebkuru e-pasta ziņojumu tieši uz PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-104">The Microsoft Print To PDF utility included in Windows 10 allows you to print any email message directly to a PDF.</span></span>

1. <span data-ttu-id="37956-105">Atlasiet ziņojumu, kuru vēlaties saglabāt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-105">Select the message you want to save.</span></span>
2. <span data-ttu-id="37956-106">Atlasiet trīs punkti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-106">Select the three dots</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="37956-107">ziņojumu un pēc tam atlasiet augšdaļā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-107">at the top of the message and then select</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="37956-108">**Drukāt**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-108">**Print**.</span></span>
3. <span data-ttu-id="37956-109">Atlasiet **Drukāt** vēlreiz un printera nolaižamajā izvēlnē atlasiet **Microsoft drukātu PDF formātā**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-109">Select **Print** again, and from the printer drop-down menu, select **Microsoft Print to PDF**.</span></span>
4. <span data-ttu-id="37956-110">Atlasiet **Drukāt**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-110">Select **Print**.</span></span>
5. <span data-ttu-id="37956-111">Ievadiet faila nosaukumu un pēc tam izvēlieties **saglabāt**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-111">Enter a file name then select **Save**.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="37956-112">**Piezīme:** Tas nav ieteicams vai koplietošanas datoros kā citi lietotāji varētu piekļūt jebkurā PDF failā, saglabājiet datorā un nedzēsiet.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37956-112">**Note:** This is not recommended on shared or public computers as other users could have access to any PDFs you save to the PC and don't delete.</span></span>
